{"tid":481823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中出論壇689講出去闖 搞gag「喺香港唔使去中國 呢度已係中國」","createTime":"2017-11-27T14:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T16:30:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b63023ae631bdd7f84f9c5867b7011697e3f903","tid":481823,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171127/large/1511778457_cd25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171127%2Flarge%2F1511778457_cd25.jpg&h=4f28f4c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年7月落台的前特首、現任全國政協副主席梁振英出席中華出入口總商會舉辦的「中出論壇」時表示，香港各產業需要「走出去」從新定位，才能更有優勢，他認為年輕人要了解其他地區，裝備自己，而不少年輕人會出去闖，但不要求每個年輕人都走出去，香港亦需要他們。。<br />\n<br />\n台下與會者發問時，認為香港年青人很需要中國的年青人來幫，中國應讓香港年青人有個基地，協助他們，交通上也要協助，中國要給香港很大幫助，香港才會有成就。梁振英笑著回應說：「我哋喺香港，唔使去中國，因為呢度已經係中國」，台下即時鼓掌附和。<br />\n梁振英認同應為年輕人提供機會，但年輕人亦應自發、主動及勤奮地去做事情，這些東西社會不應幫他們包辦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171127/57511724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171127%2F57511724&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=48306ed7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171127%2F57511724&h=a7cc5045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171127/57511724</a>"},{"pid":"d3d7f2fe5cea0dbd39c0c54c1e03ffd6376d04a1","tid":481823,"uid":22858,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中出論壇</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0969d3ee417bcff705c5bac9cf23f154c14b1eba","tid":481823,"uid":125357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"中出論壇討論中出支那女人"},{"pid":"db960d81177546cc7b6af745a822d7ff213603b2","tid":4